      <title>阿莱格拉·斯特拉顿和海伦·钱德勒-怀尔德：末日在望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-27/allegra-stratton-and-helen-chandler-wilde-the-end-is-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离大选还有七天。根据彭博社的民意调查，保守党支持率小幅下滑至 20.1%，延续了创纪录的低点，工党则轻松领先 20 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-27/allegra-stratton-and-helen-chandler-wilde-the-end-is-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院定于周一发表意见，等待特朗普案的判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-sets-monday-for-opinions-amid-wait-for-trump-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院安排周一为新的意见日 — — 并暗示任期将持续到那之后 — — 法官们将结束本轮审理，本轮审理中包括对唐纳德·特朗普总统争取刑事豁免权的争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/supreme-court-sets-monday-for-opinions-amid-wait-for-trump-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:55:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国反对国防资金谈判，激怒欧盟领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国正在敦促欧盟领导人放弃有关联合国防开支的措辞，这一立场引发了其他成员国的抵制，他们认为需要额外的资源来提升欧盟的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-irks-eu-leaders-by-opposing-talks-on-how-to-fund-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱伊的改革将在阿根廷国会迈向终点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/milei-s-reforms-set-to-cross-finish-line-in-argentina-s-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱即将取得上任以来的最大政治胜利，议员们很可能会最终批准两项旨在重振阿根廷危机经济的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/milei-s-reforms-set-to-cross-finish-line-in-argentina-s-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若欧洲央行降低法国债券收益率，德国可能表示反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 表示，如果法国立法选举引发该国政府债券的危险抛售，欧洲央行的干预可能是非法的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/germany-may-object-if-ecb-moves-to-lower-french-bond-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党大选后获得数十亿美元私人投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/labour-expects-billions-of-private-investment-after-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 计划在工党执政的头几个月内向英国引入价值数十亿英镑的新私人投资 —— 反对党希望这笔投资足以帮助其实现雄心勃勃的增长目标，并避免在赢得下周的选举后实施大规模增税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/labour-expects-billions-of-private-investment-after-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基参加峰会 乌克兰赢得欧盟安全协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/ukraine-wins-eu-security-deal-as-zelenskiy-joins-leaders-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基与欧盟签署了一项长期安全承诺协议，西方盟友承诺继续为基辅提供军事和政治支持。]]></description>
